```
name: CI for Unit tests
on:
    push:
        branches: [ main ] ![1](assets/1.png)
    pull_request:
        branches: [ main ] ![2](assets/2.png)
jobs:
    unit-tests:
      timeout-minutes: 60
      runs-on: ubuntu-latest
      steps:
      - uses: actions/checkout@v3   ![3](assets/3.png)
      - uses: actions/setup-node@v3 ![4](assets/4.png)
        with:
          node-version: 18
      - name: Install dependencies ![5](assets/5.png)
        run: npm i
      - name: Execute unit tests
        run: npm run test:coverage ![6](assets/6.png)
      - name: Uploading artifacts ![7](assets/7.png)
        uses: actions/upload-artifact@v3
        with:
          name: test-results
          path: test-results/
          retention-days: 30
```
